{
  "stem": "1860.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was even an incidental where a single girl became pregnant in Emalia, while we were already living there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Schindler arranged for a-- an abortion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this is unheard of because normally a girl like this would have been shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But one could approach Schindler and trust him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You-- you spoke to him like to-- to-- to a good uncle, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember any-- I really couldn't say anything-- anything bad about him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once we were-- once he create-- once he created the sub-camp, and we were detained in Emalia, yes, we worked-- then he converted the enamelware factory into an ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while I worked on a machine that was making threads on a certain metal parts was a precision machine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was my-- my job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, I was in a little different situation knowing that my-- my-- my father and my brother are safe, in a way.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was always hoping that this will end, and we will be reunited.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the meantime, after work, we would always-- we were talking with-- women were in separate barracks and men were in separate barracks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you were maybe surprised, but in the evening we were even singing and telling jokes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were trying to-- to-- to keep ourselves alive in a relatively good-- I don't know if it's a good mood, but make it bearable for us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And besides we were not all the time frightened with having Schindler around us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a tremendous comfort.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in-- with Schindler on Emalia we were until October 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he was moved-- he moved the factory to Brunnlitz in Sudetenland, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And the-- he said that his workers are indispensable.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
